title: Tom Clancy's Rainbow Six & Eagle Watch
description:
The series that started it all, Tom Clancy's Rainbow Six is considered the most realistic tactical shooter to ever be released with strategic planning to realistic weaponry. From simple terrrorist take downs to hostage rescue, Rainbow Six brings the Tom Clancy world of techno-thriller to the PC where the player can participate in it.

To install, simply mount and install (use compatibility mode for Vista/Seven users). Install the original before installing Eagle Watch expansion.

Language: English
